        "<li><a href=\"http://www.trancegoa.org/l,trancegoa,12,,1.html\" target=\"blank\">Trancegoa</a>: French trance lovers offering and seeking car travels as accommodation:"
        "</li>"
        "</ul>"
        "</p>"

